{{Use dmy dates|date=August 2016}} {{Infobox film | name = Ukrainian Sheriffs | image = Ukrainian Sheriffs.jpg | caption = Film poster | director = [[Roman Bondarchuk]] | producer = | writer = Roman Bondarchuk | starring = | music = | cinematography = | editing = | distributor = | released = {{Film date|2015|11|20|[[International Documentary Film Festival Amsterdam|IDFA]]|df=yes}} | runtime = 88 minutes | country = Ukraine | language = Ukrainian | budget = }}
'''''Ukrainian Sheriffs''''' ({{lang-uk|'''Українські шерифи'''}}) is a 2015 Ukrainian [[documentary film]] directed by [[Roman Bondarchuk]].<ref name="review">{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/ukrainian-sheriffs-idfa-review-846198 |title='Ukrainian Sheriffs': IDFA Review |work=[[The Hollywood Reporter]] |date=7 December 2015 |accessdate=31 August 2016}}</ref><ref name="life">{{cite web|url=http://life.pravda.com.ua/culture/2016/08/31/217458/ |title=Обрано три фільми-кандидати на "Оскар" від України |work=[[Ukrayinska Pravda]] |language=Ukrainian |date=31 August 2016 |accessdate=31 August 2016}}</ref> It was selected as the Ukrainian entry for the [[Academy Award for Best Foreign Language Film|Best Foreign Language Film]] at the [[89th Academy Awards]] but it was not nominated.<ref name="Ukraine">{{cite web|url=http://life.pravda.com.ua/culture/2016/09/9/217833/ |title=На "Оскар" від України номінували фільм "Українські шерифи" |work=[[Ukrayinska Pravda]] |language=Ukrainian |date=9 September 2016 |accessdate=9 September 2016}}</ref><ref name="UT">{{cite web|url=http://uatoday.tv/entertainment/ukraine-selects-its-candidate-for-foreign-language-oscar-743635.html |title=Ukraine selects its candidate for foreign-language Oscar |work=[[Ukraine Today]] |date=9 September 2016 |accessdate=9 September 2016}}</ref><ref name="HWR">{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/oscars-ukraine-selects-ukrainian-sheriffs-926915 |title=Oscars: Ukraine Selects 'Ukrainian Sheriffs' for Foreign-Language Category |work=[[The Hollywood Reporter]] |date=9 September 2016 |accessdate=9 September 2016}}</ref>
